  "texts": [
    "This personalized and adaptive approach has the potential to provide more effective pain relief and minimize the risk of adverse effects [161].",
    "This review is mainly limited to adults and excluded pediatric populations.",
    "The applications of AI for automated pain assessment are very beneficial in the most vulnerable groups of patients, e.g., pediatrics, geriatric patients with dementia, intellectual disability and unconscious patients.",
    "However, those most vulnerable groups were not included in this review.",
    "This is a narrative review and not a prospective study or a systematic review."
  ]
}